    Z "Esos golpes son tan patéticos que hasta a mí me dan pena."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:646
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_4d674893:

    # Z "Don't worry... you'll join him soon."
    Z "No te preocupes... pronto te unirás a él."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:647
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_ba890a96:

    # Z "But when that happens, I don't expect you to wake up again."
    Z "Pero cuando eso pase, no espero que vuelvas a despertarte."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:651
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_e455ce1f:

    # Ban "Still able to talk, huh? Perhaps I should aim for the teeth..."
    Ban "¿Todavía puedes hablar, eh? Quizás debería apuntar a los dientes..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:654
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_07bf13d7:

    # Ban3 "I'm sure Father won't mind. He only needs the [persistent.da]."
    Ban3 "Estoy seguro de que al Padre no le importará. Solo necesita a la [persistent.da]."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:655
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_963ce1c2:

    # Ban "What do you think, Stalker? Is she getting her face beaten in, or has her new owner convinced her of a better fate, yet?"
    Ban "¿Qué crees, Acechador? ¿Le están reventando la cara o su nuevo dueño ya la ha convencido de un destino mejor?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:656
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_bd7e803f:

    # Ban3 "I say you beat {i}his{/i} face in a little more."
    Ban3 "Yo digo que le des un poco más a {i}su{/i} cara."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:659
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_4bff11e5:

    # Ne "STOP IT!!"
    Ne "¡¡BASTA!!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:663
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_e42ef78a:

    # Ne "You're going too far!"
    Ne "¡Os estáis pasando!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:666
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_d515c7bd:

    # Ne "If [S] finds out what you're doing to him, you can forget whatever disgusting thing your Father wanted from her!"
    Ne "¡Si [S] se entera de lo que le estáis haciendo, podéis olvidaros de lo que vuestro Padre quiera de ella!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:669
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_0722dd43:

    # Ban "Look who can't help but run her mouth again."
    Ban "Mira quién no puede evitar abrir la boca de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:670
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_404e939a:

    # Ban3 "Didn't we tell you to sit back and shut it?!"
    Ban3 "¿No te dijimos que te sentaras y cerraras el pico?!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:673
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_9ab87f90:

    # Ne "Just... hold out a little longer."
    Ne "Solo... aguanta un poco más."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:676
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_436a8611:

    # Ne "We will get out of here... right?"
    Ne "Vamos a salir de aquí... ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:679
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_70408345:

    # Ban "Rahil... you know how to handle her."
    Ban "Rahil... tú sabes cómo manejarla."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:682
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_dfc8faa9:

    # Rah "What did I say..."
    Rah "Qué fue lo que te dije..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:686
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_42f36315:

    # Ne "Aaahhh!"
    Ne "¡Aaahhh!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:687
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_2622f125:

    # Rah "...JUST FIVE MINUTES AGO?!"
    Rah "... ¡¿HACE SOLO CINCO MINUTOS?!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:690
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_6d5f255a:

    # Rah "Come here, you stupid brat!"
    Rah "¡Ven aquí, mocosa estúpida!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:691
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_211ca0b1:

    # Rah "Father will forgive me, I need to teach you a real lesson..."
    Rah "Padre me perdonará, necesito darte una lección de verdad..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:693
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_ed847f90:

    # C "No, he will not."
    C "No, no te perdonará."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:696
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_b9d7ebc3:

    # C "Not unless you want to end up next to this guy..."
    C "A menos que quieras terminar al lado de este tipo..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:699
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_57f7e5ac:

    # Rah "But... she won't sit tight, and she keeps running her stupid mouth."
    Rah "Pero... no se está quieta y no para de soltar estupideces."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:700
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_23488b3a:

    # Rey "Then tie her up?! I know you enjoy when they struggle, you sick fuck."
    Rey "¡¿Pues átala?! Sé que disfrutas cuando se resisten, maldito pervertido."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:701
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_2d192db2:

    # Rey "Now put her in the corner, before I tell Father how you treat our prisoners!"
    Rey "¡Ahora ponla en un rincón, antes de que le diga al Padre cómo tratas a nuestros prisioneros!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:704
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_434698dd:

    # Rah "Fine..."
    Rah "Vale..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:707
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_6e55da1f:

    # Rah "Get down, and don't move an inch!"
    Rah "¡Siéntate y no te muevas ni un centímetro!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:709
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_e1ea8455:

    # Ne "Ah!"
    Ne "¡Ah!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:712
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_ea3521ce:

    # Ne "Mnnh...!"
    Ne "¡Mnnh...!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:713
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_736d0313:

    # Rah "Still now, witch..."
    Rah "Quédate quieta ahora, bruja..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:716
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_ca26a835:

    # Rey "Gods be damned... looks like they fucked you up good."
    Rey "Malditos dioses... parece que te han dado una buena paliza."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:719
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_92a71bc5:

    # Rey "I haven't had a chance to tell you what's going on, have I?"
    Rey "No he tenido la oportunidad de contarte qué está pasando, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:722
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_32948078:

    # Rey "See, back in the zone, your [persistent.da] thought it was a good idea to kill three of our men and cut my hand off."
    Rey "Verás, allá en la zona, tu [persistent.da] pensó que era buena idea matar a tres de nuestros hombres y cortarme la mano."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:723
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_4f5c7a28:

    # Rey "And then she took my bike and left."
    Rey "Y luego se llevó mi moto y se largó."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:726
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_4ff4ac96:

    # Rey "Unfortunately for her, and you, I made it back home to my tribe..."
    Rey "Desgraciadamente para ella, y para ti, logré volver a casa con mi tribu..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:727
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_515979ad:

    # Rey "...and after Father decided to \"convince\" that spineless coward Domitius for some tribute, some of us came to collect and noticed a new face."
    Rey "... y después de que Padre decidiera \"convencer\" a ese cobarde sin espina de Domitius para que pagara tributo, algunos vinimos a cobrar y nos fijamos en una cara nueva."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:728
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_64e6a8fb:

    # Rey "We did a little snooping around, followed you around, and voila..."
    Rey "Indagamos un poco, os seguimos, y voilà..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:729
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_5e1b05cf:

    # Rey "A rich Stalker, his fat truck, and a bonus on top! That bitch who took my fucking hand! How could we say no?!"
    Rey "¡Un Acechador rico, su camionaza, y de propina, esa zorra que me quitó la maldita mano! ¡¿Cómo íbamos a decir que no?!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:732
translate spanish d20a_mc_phase_1_8002ff54:

    # Rey "And now, we're here. How quickly things can change, am I right?"
    Rey "Y ahora, estamos aquí. Qué rápido cambian las cosas, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:737
translate spanish d20a152_a784cb4a:

    # Z "Where is my [persistent.da]? And what do you want from her?!"
    Z "¿Dónde está mi [persistent.da]? ¡¿Y qué queréis de ella?!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:740
translate spanish d20a152_7f1e2072:

    # Rey "Isn't it obvious? Father likes her. He likes to claim a new girl from time to time."
    Rey "¿No es obvio? Al Padre le gusta. Le gusta reclamar una chica nueva de vez en cuando."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:741
translate spanish d20a152_c2d26e40:

    # Rey "Who knows, maybe he's already fucking her?"
    Rey "Quién sabe, ¿quizás ya se la está follando?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:744
translate spanish d20a152_e300d65c:

    # Rey "What's that face? It's the best thing you can hope for... a chance for the two of you to actually survive this."
    Rey "¿Qué cara es esa? Es lo mejor que puedes esperar... una oportunidad para que los dos sobreviváis a esto de verdad."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:750
translate spanish d20a152_72006337:

    # Z "[S] let you live, and this is how you thank her?!"
    Z "¡¿[S] te dejó con vida, y así es como se lo agradeces?!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:751
translate spanish d20a152_875fd214:

    # Z "But then... I am sure she will address that mistake."
    Z "Pero bueno... estoy seguro de que ella rectificará ese error."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:754
translate spanish d20a152_ee266215:

    # Rey "Empty threats... do you know how many men have been in your position before?"
    Rey "Amenazas vacías... ¿sabes cuántos hombres han estado en tu posición antes?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:757
translate spanish d20a152_fbba0f7b:

    # Z "You should have retired after the Zone. Now you're going to lose your other hand, too, if you're lucky."
    Z "Deberías haberte retirado después de la Zona. Ahora vas a perder la otra mano también, si tienes suerte."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:760
translate spanish d20a152_a643afd2:

    # Rey "Empty threats from a man whose face is so bloodied I can't even recognise it."
    Rey "Amenazas vacías de un hombre que tiene la cara tan ensangrentada que ni siquiera la reconozco."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:763
translate spanish d20a152_885c0b44:

    # Rey "...but then, you're just as arrogant as your pretentious [persistent.da]. Don't know when you're beat."
    Rey "... pero en fin, eres tan arrogante como tu pretencioso [persistent.da]. No sabes cuándo estás acabado."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:767
translate spanish d20a152_e8ab177a:

    # Ban3 "So... what now, Reyna?"
    Ban3 "Entonces... ¿qué hacemos ahora, Reyna?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:768
translate spanish d20a152_61cf5efb:

    # Rey "If he's able to talk, he's able to take another round."
    Rey "Si puede hablar, puede aguantar otra ronda."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:771
translate spanish d20a152_32a86da6:

    # Rey "See that spot above his left eye? You can make it look worse. I'm taking a break."
    Rey "¿Ves ese moratón encima de su ojo izquierdo? Podéis hacer que parezca peor. Yo me tomo un descanso."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:772
translate spanish d20a152_929e5db8:

    # Rey "Have fun, boys..."
    Rey "Divertíos, chicos..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:775
translate spanish d20a152_e40d8f90:

    # "The two men let out a low, mirthless laugh, as they step towards you..."
    "Los dos hombres sueltan una risa baja y sin alegría, mientras dan un paso hacia ti..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:778
translate spanish d20a152_726093b6:

    # "Meanwhile..."
    "Mientras tanto..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:781
translate spanish d20a152_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Algún tiempo después..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:788
translate spanish d20a152_726093b6_1:

    # "Meanwhile..."
    "Mientras tanto..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:791
translate spanish d20a152_33a46fdf_1:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Algún tiempo después..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:799
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_c2f2779e:

    # "He tries to compose himself, as Father angrily storms out..."
    "El intenta recomponerse, mientras Padre sale furioso..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:802
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_4c4720f7:

    # Ban2 "I... told you to play nice..."
    Ban2 "Yo... te dije que te portaras bien..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:803
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_81d08c4a:

    # Ban2 "See this?! This is your fault!"
    Ban2 "¡¿Ves esto?! ¡Esto es culpa tuya!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:806
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_9fcce5a5:

    # S "My fault? For what? Saying no to your...-"
    S "¿Culpa mía? ¿Por qué? ¿Por decirle que no a tu...?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:809
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_c7a755bb:

    # Ban2 "SHUT... your sneaky little mouth, for once."
    Ban2 "CIERRA... esa boca astuta de una vez."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:812
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_d76195b9:

    # Ban2 "You think you can just walk in here, huh..."
    Ban2 "Crees que puedes entrar aquí así como así, eh..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:813
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_5db94271:

    # Ban2 "...then refuse Father... get me all fucked up..."
    Ban2 "... luego decirle que no al Padre...  dejarme hecho mierda... "

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:816
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_abbce16c:

    # Ban2 "...I've had enough with you."
    Ban2 "... ya estoy harto de ti."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:819
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_4cabc3db:

    # Ban2 "Father won't let me have you... but he won't say anything against a good beating."
    Ban2 "Padre no me dejará tenerte... pero no dirá nada contra una buena paliza."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:823
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_17f5170e:

    # Ban2 "Ready to feel what I'm feeling, Stalker whore?!"
    Ban2 "¿Lista para sentir lo que yo siento, puta Acechadora?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:827
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_6f54469a:

    # S "Hhngh-!"
    S "¡Hhngh-!"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:828
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_8bb73cfd:

    # Ban2 "That's what I thought..."
    Ban2 "Eso es lo que pensaba..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:836
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_681139a1:

    # S "Agh..."
    S "Agh..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:837
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_16660b06:

    # Ban2 "{i}*laughs*{/i}"
    Ban2 "{i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:840
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_ebcacbba:

    # Ban2 "Should've sucked his dick instead..."
    Ban2 "Deberías habérsela chupado en su lugar..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:846
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_59b844ee:

    # S "Nnh..."
    S "Nnh..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:859
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_64d64c77:

    # Ban2 "It's done."
    Ban2 "Está hecho."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:862
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_1a3c4847:

    # Ban2 "I have been looking forward to this moment."
    Ban2 "Llevo tiempo esperando este momento."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:863
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_de8d81e6:

    # Bfa "To see your victory spoiled? This could have been your trophy, had you not pussied out."
    Bfa "¿Para ver cómo te arruinan la victoria? Esto podría haber sido tu trofeo, si no te hubieras acojonado."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:864
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_ab25ee5d:

    # Bfa "Instead, you get to sit back and watch, like the worm you are."
    Bfa "En cambio, te toca quedarte mirando, como el gusano que eres."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:867
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_c1933b81:

    # St "Have I become numb to their degrading words..."
    St "Me he vuelto insensible a sus palabras degradantes..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:868
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_ca1cbc01:

    # St "...or is it because I am on my knees in front of this man?"
    St "... ¿o es porque estoy de rodillas delante de este hombre?"

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:871
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_3c2dd1b6:

    # St "He's staring at my chest, I know it..."
    St "Me está mirando el pecho, lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:874
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_d67ed6ad:

    # Bfa "She's a fine woman, indeed."
    Bfa "Es una mujer espléndida, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:875
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_76a08b69:

    # Ban2 "She is... but I prefer them more docile."
    Ban2 "Lo es... pero yo las prefiero más dóciles."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:876
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_739bafa8:

    # Bfa "Fierce is good. All the more fun to break her."
    Bfa "Que sea feroz es bueno. Así da más gusto quebrantarla."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:879
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_17831e5c:

    # St "How did I get to this... kneeling before him as if defeated in battle..."
    St "¿Cómo he llegado a esto... de rodillas ante él como si me hubiera derrotado en combate..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:880
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_3dabc710:

    # Bfa "You have a choice here, Stalker."
    Bfa "Tienes una elección aquí, Acechadora."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:881
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_06e70345:

    # Bfa "Deny your new place, and my son will put you back in chains. In time, we will bring the heads of your friends here, to keep you company."
    Bfa "Niega tu nuevo lugar, y mi hijo te volverá a poner las cadenas. Con el tiempo, traeremos las cabezas de tus amigos aquí, para que te hagan compañía."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:884
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_df7bdf4f:

    # Bfa "Or you take the reasonable route, and submit like custom demands. If you make me believe it, your friends might just live."
    Bfa "O tomas el camino razonable y te sometes como exige la costumbre. Si me haces creerlo, tus amigos quizás vivan."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:885
translate spanish d20a_shani_phase_2_827e571d:

    # Bfa "There's no dishonour in that."
    Bfa "No hay deshonor en ello."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:891
translate spanish d20a105_ea5c2164:

    # St "I will never give myself to him."
    St "Nunca me entregaré a él."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:894
translate spanish d20a105_bc90d931:

    # S "Talk to me again about custom and honour... Some of us live by them, and you never faced me in combat nor bested me."
    S "Vuelve a hablarme de costumbres y honor... Algunos vivimos por y para ellos, y tú jamás te enfrentaste a mí en combate ni me venciste."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:895
translate spanish d20a105_5ff79d55:

    # S "Step closer, and I'll still kick your head in. So keep dreaming."
    S "Acércate y aún te reventaré la cabeza. Así que sigue soñando."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:898
translate spanish d20a105_8565964f:

    # Bfa "..."
    Bfa "..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:901
translate spanish d20a105_06f5f460:

    # Bfa "Fierce you are, indeed."
    Bfa "Feroz eres, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:904
translate spanish d20a105_9af36b24:

    # Bfa "Have it your way. My son will give you the same treatment the old man is getting. Maybe that will soften your resolve."
    Bfa "Como quieras. Mi hijo te dará el mismo trato que está recibiendo el viejo. Quizás eso ablande tu resolución."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:905
translate spanish d20a105_02748544:

    # Bfa "Until then, you are good for nothing. I have no need or desire for a rebellious slave."
    Bfa "Hasta entonces, no sirves para nada. No necesito ni quiero una esclava rebelde."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:908
translate spanish d20a105_d0cd093c:

    # Bfa "Son... don't fail me again. Put her back against the wall."
    Bfa "Hijo... no me falles otra vez. Ponla contra la pared."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:909
translate spanish d20a105_1800681a:

    # Ban2 "Yes, Father."
    Ban2 "Sí, padre."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:924
translate spanish d20a113_968fce39:

    # St "I can't risk putting them in danger..."
    St "No puedo arriesgarme a ponerlos en peligro..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:925
translate spanish d20a113_a381ff74:

    # Bfa "You have made your decision, then."
    Bfa "Entonces ya has tomado tu decisión."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:929
translate spanish d20a113_5d9c84f3:

    # Bfa "You have talked enough now. It's time for you to submit."
    Bfa "Ya has hablado bastante. Es hora de que te sometas."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:932
translate spanish d20a113_04ed9dfe:

    # St "It's... right in front of me..."
    St "Está... justo delante de mí..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:933
translate spanish d20a113_f49ceff9:

    # St "I'm going to have take it into my mouth like a common slave..."
    St "Voy a tener que metérmela en la boca como una esclava cualquiera..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:934
translate spanish d20a113_ca0adaef:

    # Bfa "Open your mouth. Show me your tongue."
    Bfa "Abre la boca. Muéstrame la lengua."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:937
translate spanish d20a113_a756fdde:

    # Bfa "I won't ask twice."
    Bfa "No lo pediré dos veces."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:938
translate spanish d20a113_d871cac8:

    # St "I have to stay on top of this, but..."
    St "Tengo que mantener el control, pero..."

# game/scripts/day20.rpy:939
translate spanish d20a113_5b0b59fe:

